<p>1. Dominate is a mobile app, created by IGN that will allow users to share their gameing experiences with others.  In addition to being a mobile app, users will also be able to share via a PC Console and is in the works of being available on multiple platofrms and social media.  The developers chose to use PhoneGap becuase of its mobile platofrom availability and its device specific functions.  
